  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain the ability to decipher an opponent’s tactics and develop a counter to them. As a bonus action, you make a Wisdom (<strong>Insight</strong>) check against a creature you can see that isn’t <strong>incapacitated</strong>, contested by the target’s Charisma (<strong>Deception</strong>) check. If you succeed, you can use your @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.ZNG4a61hajMEzhb1]{Sneak Attack} against that target even if you don't have <strong>advantage</strong> on the attack roll, but not if you have <strong>disadvantage</strong> on it.</p><p>This benefit lasts for 1 minute or until you successfully use this feature against a different target.</p>",
